Small aeroplanes are able to land on small and commuter airports without crashing as frequently as the larger ones. A useful technique is to override the colour of small aircraft to something different to your default, which makes them easy to spot when you build aircraft.

== 飞机事故 ==
[[File:en/Manual/Crashed airplane.png|200px|thumb|left|一架坠毁的飞机]]

[[File:en/Manual/Mass-crash.png|200px|thumb|right|没有可降落的机场时]] 

飞机降落机场时有小几率坠毁。这会阻挡它降落的跑道一段时间，并lower your ratings at the airport considerably.

飞机降落机场时默认有极小几率坠毁(0.07%)。除此之外，大型飞机在''小型''或''通勤''机场降落时有较大几率（5%）坠毁。The amount of these random plane crashes can be configured in the advanced settings under Disasters/Accidents -> Number of plane crashes (Advanced Settings).

在一个运输公司的所有机场被移除后，公司的飞机会集体坠毁（actually when the ghost station that remains after destroying the airport has disappeared also)。这些飞机会在空中爆炸并坠毁。

飞机事故可在 高级设置 菜单完全关闭（Advanced settings -> Disasters/Accidents -> Number of plane crashes -> set to "none"）。

